      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours-ready condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The mechanical provenance is exhaustive: rod bearing replacement is documented, the VANOS system has been bulletproofed with overhauled solenoids, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension maintains factory-spec kinematics with refreshed bushings and dampers, while the M-Variable differential provides optimal lockup. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic, the paint depth is exceptional, showing no signs of orange peel or rock chips. Inside, the Nappa leather bolsters are firm and free of typical wear. This is a turn-key, purist-spec machine for the collector who values atmospheric induction and analog feedback.",
