      "description": "Presenting an absolute gem: a meticulously maintained vehicle that remains in true showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero chips, swirls, or imperfections, protected by a recent ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin retains that 'new car' scent, featuring flawless hand-stitched leather upholstery, untouched trim, and every technological feature functioning as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is peerless; it has been garage-kept since day one and serviced exclusively at the dealership with a comprehensive paper trail included. From the pristine engine bay to the brand-new performance tires, no detail has been overlooked. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle of unparalleled quality.",
